    <discussion><h4><openfilelink filename="SP-Tools Overview.maxpat">Open the Overview Patch</openfilelink></h4>
The <o>sp.realtimeframe~</o> object is the counterpart to <o>sp.onsetframe~</o> where instead of outputting the frame to analyzed based on onset detection, <o>sp.realtimeframe~</o> spits out a constant stream of frame values to analyze enabling realtime analysis of multiple descriptor types that remain in sync.
</discussion>

